tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE DeliveryRoutes (
  route_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  origin VARCHAR(50),
  destination VARCHAR(50),
  distance FLOAT,
  delivery_time TIMESTAMP
)
CREATE TABLE delivery_routes (route_id INT, start_location VARCHAR(255), end_location VARCHAR(255), distance FLOAT, delivery_time TIMESTAMP)
CREATE TABLE route_history (history_id INT, route_id INT, analyzed_date DATE, average_delivery_time FLOAT, optimization_results TEXT)

CREATE TABLE delivery_routes (
    route_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    driver_id INT,
    route_date DATE,
    start_location VARCHAR(255),
    end_location VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE delivery_history (
    delivery_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    route_id INT,
    delivery_date DATE,
    delivery_time TIME,
    delivery_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE driver_performance (
    driver_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    total_deliveries INT,
    missed_deliveries INT,
    avg_delivery_time TIME,
    rating DECIMAL(3,2)
);

CREATE TABLE delivery_routes (
	route_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	start_location VARCHAR(255),
	end_location VARCHAR(255),
	distance FLOAT,
	time_taken INT
)

CREATE TABLE delivery_history (
	history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	route_id INT,
	date DATE,
	delivery_status VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE delivery_vehicles (
	vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	vehicle_type VARCHAR(50),
	max_capacity INT,
	current_load INT
)

CREATE TABLE delivery_agents (
	agent_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	agent_name VARCHAR(100),
	agent_phone VARCHAR(15),
	agent_email VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE delivery_costs (
	cost_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	route_id INT,
	vehicle_id INT,
	cost FLOAT
)
